title: #LiveOutside2016 Rio de Janeiro Episode 4
description:
Beach culture is a huge part of everyday life in Rio. Get a first-hand look at the surf and the style of Rio’s most iconic beaches and take a 360 degree tour of the Seralon stairs and Arpoador rock overlooking Ipanema Beach. 

Music: "King of the Beach" by The Wavves
